      <title>ゼネラリストから「連続スペシャリスト」へ</title>
      <link>https://meganii.com/blog/2014/11/03/specialist-work-shift/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Nov 2014 15:25:00 +0900</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://meganii.com/blog/2014/11/03/specialist-work-shift/</guid>
